data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER****BRING OFFERS!  Large 2-bedroom Admirals Cove home with an extra room (with closet) and office. Spacious living room for entertaining.  Large kitchen with ample cabinet space and connects to the dining space. Welcoming covered front porch, fully fenced yard and patio for entertaining. Plenty of parking for friends. Community clubhouse with pool. Quiet neighborhood conveniently located near Mukilteo and Port Townsend ferries. New roof prior to closing.
